,
128
,
256
 and K‚ÄØ=‚ÄØ2,‚ÄØ3 show strong Pearson/Spearman correlations (>‚ÄØ0.80) with extremely low p‚Äëvalues, confirming baseline behaviour holds at scale.

Adaptive œÑ Refinement ‚Äî œÑ is now dynamically computed (0.00095) from ensemble percentile bands, ensuring live stability control across the Œ≤‚Äëband.

