.

The Œ∫ you choose is the smallest that passes, preserving the most acceptance strictness with acceptable mixing.

YAML delta for both
yaml
updates:
  geometry_driven:
    shard_mapping:
      adjacency_source: "polytope_graph"
      allow_two_hop: true
      p_one_hop: 0.90
      p_two_hop: 0.10
      cache_volumes: true
