\begin{itemize}
  \item $\kappa$ seeded at 5.0 with ESS‚Äëaware auto‚Äëselection.
  \item Guard polynomial $\beta^4 - 3\beta^2 + 2$ holds over $\beta \in [0.3934,0.3990]$.
\end{itemize}

\medskip
